type(scope): brief description of changes

# REQUIRED FORMAT: type(scope): description
# 
# Types: feat, fix, chore, docs, style, refactor, test, build, ci
# Scopes: argocd, cert-manager, clusters, deploy, eso, externaldns, netscaler, 
#         ollama, open-webui, olmv0, adcs-issuer, setup, utils, docs, multiple
# 
# Rules:
# - First line: type(scope): description (max 72 chars)
# - Type must be one of the allowed types above
# - Scope is required and must be in parentheses
# - Colon and space after closing parenthesis
# - Description must not start with a space or capital letter
# 
# Valid examples:
# feat(argocd): add operator-based deployment
# fix(deploy): correct namespace creation logic
# chore(multiple): update ALLOW_LIST configurations
# docs(readme): add deployment instructions
#
# Invalid examples:
# feat: missing scope - INVALID
# feat(argocd) missing colon - INVALID  
# feat(argocd):  extra space after colon - INVALID
# feat(argocd): Description starts with capital - INVALID
